<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2637358>
    dc:description "FIGURE 9. A. Altavelia amoena (junior synonym of A. flavomarginata), male, dorsal view. B. Altavelia flavomarginata, male, dorsal view. C. Altavelia inveruglas, male, dorsal view. D. Altavelia osborniana, female, dorsal view" ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/2637358/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2637346>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. A. Altavelia montana, thorax and base of abdomen, ventral view; white arrows show position of central tubercles. B. Altavelia flavomarginata, female, apex of thorax and abdomen, dorsal view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/2637346/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2637352>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. A. Altavelia boliviana, male, dorsal view. B. Altavelia boliviana, female, apex of abdomen, left posterolateral view. C. Altavelia columbiensis, male, dorsal view. D. Altavelia columbiensis, male, lateral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/2637352/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

